Requirements/Dependencies:

- M2Crypto
- requests
- urlparse
- protobuf

Install Payment Request Protobuf:

protoc --proto_path=plugins/lib/ --python_out=plugins/lib/ plugins/lib/paymentrequest.proto

(Docs: https://developers.google.com/protocol-buffers/docs/reference/python-generated)

Install CA-Bundle for Signature Verification:

http://curl.haxx.se/docs/caextract.html

Either download the provided pem file, or use a tool to create your own.  The file should be placed at ~/.electrum/ca/ca-bundle.crt


